al. Documentation If an incident occurs in a workplace (including a marine environment), it must be documented properly. The documentation may be paper and/ or electronic. The reports you create are official legal documents: paper versions should be filled out in pen (not pencil), with any changes or corrections crossed out and initialed. Good documentation is: • Complete and accurate • Objective • Completed as soon as possible (while your memory of the incident Responding to Emergencies.",
