sk of insect stings: • Wear a long-sleeved shirt, long pants, and closed-toe shoes. • Don’t wear perfume, cologne, or other products with strong scents. • Remove or cover items that will attract insects, such as garbage or What to Look For What to Do Call EMS/9-1-1 and get an AED if there are any signs of a severe allergic Poisons167.",
